               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18170416-138-person1059">
                  ROBERT 
                  WILD
               <interp inst="t18170416-138-person1059" type="surname" value="WILD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170416-138-person1059" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170416-138-person1059" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am shopman to Mr. Sowerby, <rs id="t18170416-138-viclabel722" type="occupation">pawnbroker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170416-138-victim1058 t18170416-138-viclabel722"></join>, <placeName id="t18170416-138-crimeloc723">Chiswell-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18170416-138-crimeloc723" type="placeName" value="Chiswell-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18170416-138-crimeloc723" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170416-138-off720 t18170416-138-crimeloc723"></join>. On 21st of March, at three o'clock in the afternoon, I observed the shadow of a man. I went to the door, and saw the prisoner in the shop, as far as the door would screen him - I am sure he is the man. About half past four o'clock, I saw him at the door again. I saw him pull the scarf a little way throught the string at the door, and go away. He came again, and pulled it nearly off in about five minutes, he came again, and took it quite off - I collared him on the step.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18170416-138-person1060">
                  JOSHUA 
                  ARMSTRONG
               <interp inst="t18170416-138-person1060" type="surname" value="ARMSTRONG"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170416-138-person1060" type="given" value="JOSHUA"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170416-138-person1060" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took the prisoner into custody, and found a waistcoat and two flutes concealed upon him.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
